casebody.data:
Cynthia M. MCINERNEY, Respondent,
v.
Patrick A. MCINERNEY, Appellant. WD 81285 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: May 14, 2019 Jonathan Sternbert, Kansas City, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Preston Drobeck, Kansas City, MO, Counsel for Respondent. Before Division Three: Thomas H. Newton, Presiding Judge, Alok Ahuja, and Edward R. Ardini, Judges

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Mr. Patrick A. McInerney appeals a Jackson County Circuit Court judgment denying his first amended motion to modify child support. For reasons stated in the memorandum provided to the parties, we affirm. Rule 84.16(b).
